<C>__{ann}
<D>__{my life is...shit. it's all shit. it's like somebody saying, "okay, chairs are not chairs, they're actually swimming pools" i mean, nothing is what i thought it was. what happened to me? have i been asleep? i vaguely remember the wedding, but a lot of it is just a blur...like i was watching from a distance. i can't believe him. why didn't i trust my intuition?}
