<C>__{ann}
<D>__{and i'm vacuuming his goddam rug. his rug, that he paid to have put in his house. nothing in that place belongs to me. i wanted to put some of my grandmother's furniture in it, but he wouldn't let me. so i m vacuuming his rug. that bastard.}
